## **KEY CONFIGURATION NOTES**

1. **MD5 Authentication:** All OSPF neighbors must have `BANKOSPF2026` key
2. **Router IDs:** Must be unique (1.1.1.3, 2.2.2.3, 3.3.3.1, 3.3.3.2, 5.5.5.1, 5.5.5.2)
3. **Trunk Allowed VLANs:** Always include 10,20,30,40,50,60,70,80,99
4. **SVI Passive Interfaces:** OSPF SVIs should be passive (no hellos to servers)
5. **Access Port Security:** Unused ports shutdown and assigned to VLAN 99
6. **ASA Interface Names:** GigabitEthernet1/1 through 1/8 (NOT 0/x for Packet Tracer)
7. **Server IPs:** Use #IPCONFIG comment format in Server-PT terminal
8. **Preempt Enabled:** Ensures high-priority device reclaims active role after recovery

