## **TESTING COMMANDS**

### **Essential Verification**
```
show ip ospf neighbor                [OSPF status]
show ip bgp summary                  [BGP status]
show standby brief                   [HSRP status]
show ip nat translations             [NAT mappings]
show ip route                        [Routing table]
ping 10.0.20.254                     [Gateway connectivity]
ping 10.0.30.100                     [Server reachability]
show access-list                     [Firewall rules]
show interface trunk                 [VLAN trunk status]
show vlan brief                      [VLAN inventory]
```

