## **COMMON MISTAKES & FIXES**

| Problem | Root Cause | Fix |
|---------|-----------|-----|
| OSPF neighbors won't form | MD5 key mismatch | Verify `BANKOSPF2026` on all neighbors |
| Ping fails between VLANs | Trunk not configured | Enable trunk mode on switch ports |
| HSRP not electing | SVI down | Create VLAN SVI first |
| Firewall blocking good traffic | Wrong ACL rules | Review access-list and source/dest IPs |
| BGP not establishing | Neighbor IP wrong | Verify WAN IP matches peer's IP |
| NAT not working | Wrong interface | Ensure outside interface specified |

